itedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T20:53:01.000Z","msg":"推比法律巴睇呀!!!!!!!!!!<br />\n<br />\n[太子站] 有C.I.P.警狗透露有人真係死咗 希望炒車<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://lih.kg/dNREKS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://lih.kg/dNREKS</a><br />\n<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n[召喚法律巴]地鐵懷疑真係死左人2 （入嚟大家一齊判斷）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://lih.kg/dNPrDS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://lih.kg/dNPrDS</a><br />\n<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f65359ed25be6d33e12deb5965d1a8fe7ec2e4c3","tid":1528921,"uid":289649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T21:10:23.000Z","msg":"明白大家呢排嘅士氣經過<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">831恐襲</span></span>同<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">901大撤退</span></span>之後好低落<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我同大家一樣都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但越係呢啲時候<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我地就越要<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">堅持下去，團結一致</span></span><br />\n唔好比林鄭見我地冇士氣而去捉多啲人<br />\n<br />\n以下兩篇文章<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">無論<span style=\"color: gold;\">和理非</span>，定係<span style=\"color: red;\">勇武</span>，都應該入黎，打返枝<span style=\"color: violet;\">強心針</span></span><br />\n<br />\n希望可以幫到大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n記得share比身邊因近日事件而唔開心嘅朋友仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n［全部人同我入黎］《致眾表》望各位香港市民出自己的一份綿力<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1532967\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1532967</a><br />\n<br />\n灰心喪志，是因為你看不見抗爭的前路<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1533741\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1533741</a>"},{"pid":"97301880f2ad451efb773a51230d15cacf1b16a0","tid":1528921,"uid":104667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T01:05:48.000Z","msg":"麵神與我們同在"},{"pid":"32529e65b851e7a4